data.description: Nestled in the highly sought-after North Gwinnett School District, this meticulously upgraded & well maintained home offers an unparalleled living experience. Strategically positioned between the upcoming Suwanee Town Center and I-85, residents enjoy a harmonious blend of serenity and urban accessibility. Upon entering, you're welcomed by a grand two-story foyer, setting a tone of refined elegance. The layout features a versatile formal living room, ideal for an office or playroom, along with an intimate separate dining room. The kitchen is a culinary delight, boasting gorgeous white cabinets with pullout drawers and  designer-inspired leathered granite countertops. A generously sized pantry ensures ample storage, while the breakfast nook provides delightful backyard views of the large deck.  With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and finished basement space you wont want to leave home! The home includes a  owner's suite featuring an extraordinary walk-in closet and a newly renovated custom bathroom complete with a soaking tub, floating shelves, and a custom shower. Outside, you'll find that the freshly landscaped yard, adorned with blooming flowers and mulch perfectly sets the stage for outdoor gatherings this Spring & Summer. A leveled backyard offers expansion opportunities or additional entertainment space. Residents benefit from direct access to the Suwanee Greenway and George Pierce Park via walking trails, as well as proximity to Suwanee Town Center for shopping, dining, and entertainment. With top-rated schools and HOA amenities such as a pool and playground, this home seamlessly combines suburban tranquility with urban convenience.Don't let this opportunity pass you by. Schedule a showing today!
